channel.title: I Would Just Like To
channel.description:
Hi !
You might think this is a stupid post, but for some of you it might be important. I'm letting you know that i'm going to be leaving soon after this letter. I'm leaving my whole code career behind. Some of you are probably glad.
I've got lots of Thanks to say, firstly Moparisthebest. Thankyou for your wonderful forum that gave me the code career of H++. Thankyou to Mod Taharok. Such a great man ! You said that you wanted to be a Mod, god heard you i guess. And lastly, thankyou to everyone for your help with FAQ.
Thankyou for your time.
Goodbye !
